    dc:title "Vertebrate paleobiodiversity of the Early Cretaceous (Berriasian) Angeac-Charente Lagerstätte (southwestern France): implications for continental faunal turnover at the J / K boundary" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6902109>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6902105>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6902107> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6902109>
    dc:description "FIG. 31. — Reconstruction of the Angeac Ornithomimosaur, based on 3D surface scans of 232 bones. All the bones of the 3D reconstruction were scaled on the basis of a 40 cm long femur." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6902109/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6902105>
    dc:description "FIG. 29. — Ornithomimosaur remains from Angeac-Charente:A, right dentary (ANG11-776) in lateral view;B, pedal ungual (ANG11-1335) in lateral view; C, pedal ungual (ANG11-898) in lateral view; D-H, middle caudal vertebra (ANG12-1622) in dorsal (D), ventral (E), right lateral (F), anterior (G) and posterior (H) views; I-L, distal caudal vertebra (ANG14-3084) in dorsal (I), ventral (J), right lateral (K) and posterior (L) views. Scale bar: 2 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6902105/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6902107>
    dc:description "FIG. 30. — Ornithomimosaur remains from Angeac-Charente: A-C, proximal end of right tibia (ANG12-1893) in posterior (A), anterior (B) and lateral (C) views; D, distal end of right tibia (ANG10-56) in anterior view; E, proximal end of right fibula (ANG11-696) in medial view; F-H, Left astragalus and calcaneum (ANG12- 1803) in anterior (F), posterior (G) and dorsal (H) views. Scale bar: A-E, 4 cm; F-H, 2 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6902107/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

